stix:STIX_Header.stix:Title: Malicious Indicators Associated with Various Known Threats
stix:STIX_Header.stix:Description: On 5 April 2016, a trusted third-party provided a list of malicious IPv4 addresses and domains associated with known threats. According to the source, these indicators were determined to be malicious between 25 March 2016 and 31 March 2016.
